                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "Once per day, an iron cobra\u2019s creator can order it to find and kill a specific creature within 1 mile, which it does as if guided by <i>discern location</i>. The creator must have seen or be holding an item from the specified creature for this order to function."
